<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Deactivation - DentalFlow</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .deactivation-header {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .details-box {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .details-title {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #991b1b;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .details-list {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .details-list li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #7f1d1d;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
            color: #92400e;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .contact-info {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .contact-title {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #0c4a6e;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            {{#if companyLogo}}
            <img src="{{companyLogo}}" alt="{{companyName}}" class="logo">
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="deactivation-header">⚠️ Account Deactivation Notice</h2>
            
            <p>Hello {{userName}},</p>
            
            <p>We regret to inform you that your staff account at <strong>{{clinicName}}</strong> has been deactivated by the clinic administrator.</p>
            
            <div class="details-box">
                <h3 class="details-title">Account Details:</h3>
                <ul class="details-list">
                    <li><strong>Clinic:</strong> {{clinicName}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Role:</strong> {{role}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Deactivated by:</strong> {{deactivatedBy}}</li>
                    <li><strong>Deactivation Date:</strong> {{deactivationDate}}</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning">
                <strong>Important:</strong> As of this deactivation, you will no longer be able to access the clinic's patient management system or any associated services.
            </div>
            
            <p>This means:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>You cannot log in to the DentalFlow system for this clinic</li>
                <li>Your access to patient records and appointments has been revoked</li>
                <li>You will no longer receive notifications from this clinic</li>
                <li>Any pending tasks or responsibilities have been reassigned</li>
            </ul>
            
            {{#if contactEmail}}
            <div class="contact-info">
                <h4 class="contact-title">Need to Contact the Clinic?</h4>
                <p>If you have any questions about this deactivation or need to discuss your account status, please contact the clinic directly:</p>
                {{#if contactEmail}}
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{contactEmail}}">{{contactEmail}}</a></p>
                {{/if}}
                {{#if contactPhone}}
                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> {{contactPhone}}</p>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <p>If you believe this deactivation was made in error, please contact the clinic administrator immediately.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for your service at {{clinicName}}.</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>
            The {{companyName}} Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{currentYear}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>{{companyAddress}}</p>
            {{#if unsubscribeLink}}
            <p><a href="{{unsubscribeLink}}">Unsubscribe</a></p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 